      <p class="card-text"> This application will help you and your pals budget and plan for
        a vacation anywhere.</br> When we are on a trip, it might be hard to organize group spending and regulate
        personal
        finances; this app may be just what you need. </br> Anyone with an account can use this app to create a page for a vacation to project spending or to document past vacations taken with friends. We make it easy for you to
        log in details about daily budget or total trip budget. We hope to save you significant time and help you
        document the bills. We provide you easy access to document who paid for what and for which activitiy.</br> This
        application has a bonus feature to help you prepare for your vacations better! We included a weather widget for account holders to look up weather condition anywhere. 
        We hope to add more features to this application to help users map out itinairy and book for activities in future versions! </br> Have fun exploring! Oh, the places you would go~  </p>


